<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٠ - <span class="c2">(١٤٣٦)</span> وَحَدَّثَنِيهِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6904">يَحْيَى بْنُ حَبِيبٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1717">خَالِدٌ -<span class="c5"> يَعْنِي:</span> ابْنَ الْحَارِثِ </a>-، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> حَتَّى تَرْجِعَ .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>